@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "General policy, ethics, and returns";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<h2>1. General terms</h2>
<p>
    This page describes our store's general policy and ethical principles
    when working with customers, processing personal data, as well as the rules for returns
    of purchased suits and refunds.
</p>

<h2>2. Ethical principles</h2>
<ul>
    <li>We treat every customer with respect and fairness.</li>
    <li>We provide accurate and clear information about all products.</li>
    <li>We strive for honest business practices and transparent pricing.</li>
    <li>We maintain confidentiality regarding customers' personal data.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Personal data processing</h2>
<p>
    We use personal data only for:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>processing and fulfilling orders;</li>
    <li>issuing documents (invoices, warranty cards, etc.);
    </li>
    <li>contacting the customer if additional information or confirmation is needed.</li>
</ul>
<p>
    We do not share personal data with third parties unless required by law.
</p>

<h2>4. Suit return rules</h2>
<ul>
    <li>A suit can be returned within
        <strong>14 calendar days</strong> from the date of receipt.</li>
    <li>The item must be in <strong>original commercial condition</strong>:
        clean, without signs of wear, without damage, and with tags attached.</li>
    <li>Returns are not accepted for suits with visible signs of use,
        damage, or improper care.</li>
    <li>When returning an item, the customer must provide proof of purchase
        (receipt, invoice, or another supporting document).</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Refunds</h2>
<ul>
    <li>After the returned item is approved, the refund is processed
        within <strong>14 days</strong>.</li>
    <li>Refunds are made using the same payment method used for the purchase
        (bank transfer, card, or cash if applicable).</li>
    <li>For partial returns, only the value of the returned items is refunded.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Claims and defects</h2>
<ul>
    <li>If a defect is not caused by the customer, you have the right to submit a claim
        within the legally established period.</li>
    <li>In such cases, we may offer repair, replacement, or a refund.</li>
</ul>

<h2>7. Contact</h2>
<p>
    If you have questions about our policy, ethics, or return rules,
    you can contact us via the website contact form or using the listed
    phone numbers and email address.
</p>
